Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:46.23,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安土城天守 賭上明日之死鬥！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就這麼進軍的話 就能繞到從本能寺返回安土的織田大軍前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使繞到他們前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被前後夾擊的話 就毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您早就料到事會至此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓意志消沉的在下重新振作 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 那時將伊達軍解散…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都知道自已什麼時候應該以命相搏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不大喜歡這蜂擁而上的架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偶爾來這麼一次豪華的party也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show guns up！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安土城就是魔王的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可將未來交予無情無義的大將
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給予魔王的 只有往生之途！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you，guys！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還有和長政大人共建和平的選擇的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一介隨波逐流的女子 還說什麼漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有上總介大人的願望才是 我的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已將我的一切都獻給了上總介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我見兄長一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少毫無痛苦地往生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然自命“龍之右目”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那左目應該不需要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我片倉小十郎 便是雙目盡被剜去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕無意捨棄“龍之右目”之名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用你的血淚來填補我靈魂的饑渴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒吼吧！鳴神！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好熱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來滅你的火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信長大人 濃姬大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們盡情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是無法下手殺小鬼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在可是很虛弱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快些救他 就快要死掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子可不是普通的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是殺人如麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田家的武將
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智光秀 你的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 腳夠不到地面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真讓人顫慄不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在地獄裏欣賞政宗大人一統天下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再陪我玩一會兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再好好品味這現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是煉獄！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田由我們來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歸處已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後你就是孑然一身了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便到哪裡謀個活計
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿市殺掉的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪連一個門衛也沒安置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真是易守難攻的鐵壁之城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長筱之戰時受的傷又復發了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像騎馬顛簸得太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上去療傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,worry not
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小我就習慣傷痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起傷痛 更重要的是要怎樣攻入城池
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shit！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔王的新武器嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等強勁的破壞力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆頭 那是從遠處湖那邊飛來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是把西邊那群傢伙拉入伙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是個相當亂來的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝進去！真田幸村！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！筆頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你們二位的實力！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖啊！真田家的小哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方就拜託諸位了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust us！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然耍雕蟲小技混進來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殲之！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…兄長…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿市把…濃姬大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也不過就是那種程度的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是以生命為代價 從心底深愛兄長大人的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區人偶也想向餘講說三道四嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿市 不是什麼人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你便試試 貫穿吾身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…我並不是想殺你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望你能就此停手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了刺穿吾身 你已毫無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長你…好可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長…兄長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王之妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨眼…龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為長政大人的死而…哀悼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與您…戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長政大人…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼做問心無愧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨兩隻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們妄想取余頸上人頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殺你之前 我有事請教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底 是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我這隻眼中看來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是由肆虐跋扈於古今及來世的所有邪氣和魔性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所聚集而成的空具人形的怪物罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余乃織田信長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自第六天而來的魔王是也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下已清楚你的魔王之稱並非單純的名號而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個愚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將你們的頭顱做成酒杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要酒杯 就用自己的腦袋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那滿是污穢的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾滿血腥的暴虐雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將在此處 為我等封印！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拙劣的笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚者們 俯首於我吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由吾親自送你們奔赴黃泉之路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來成功衝入敵陣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田老大 獨眼龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀翔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,War Dance！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自不量力的蠢行 就以死償還吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣不分敵我地進攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的這隻眼 也由我挖出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想挖就動手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛會亮出獠牙將你緊緊咬住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱肉強食 這便是赤裸裸的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去品嘗悔恨之果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是淺井軍嗎 別急著送死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政宗…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本多忠勝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹千代家的鎧甲人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苟活下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負隅頑抗者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等卑鄙 織田信長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然只對瞄準受損鎧甲的裂口處攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要白費了他的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將他的身影 牢牢記在腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本多大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒織田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那廝絕非善類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不將其討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本國就沒有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存活下來的人們 也一定能構築起我們理想中的天下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再一次見識到你那 無愧於戰國最強之名的戰鬥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“戰國最強”之名還真是可笑至極
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰飛煙滅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好慰勞他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家康大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有餘力最後一擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你來瞭解他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下拼上性命也在所不辭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 竟還妄圖垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忤逆吾之霸道的自作聰明的螻蟻之輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富岳的大炮 精准地命中目標了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子們 給我把他們從頭到腳吃抹乾淨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 眼下實乃進軍良機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要織田滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無人能對吾等毛利家的繁榮 和安芸國的根基構成威脅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進吧 日輪之子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將魔王的城池焚盡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧州筆頭伊達政宗 推參上陣！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武田軍真田源次郎幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中烈火 永不熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前田！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 龍之右目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話待會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫一把吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最後的狂歡了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉沒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過借過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下定決心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論遇到何種情況 阿松都會伴您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿松 打完仗就麻煩你做好吃的給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾永不隕落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之道乃霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下布武是也！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last shoot了！真田幸村！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 政宗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沸騰吧！燃燒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三途黑禍生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,災厄人間盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永劫不可複
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非本無常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六天魔王織田信長葬身安土城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田家的滅亡使得亂世再起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸國群雄再次逐鹿天下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這玩意被我們的忍者部隊正式採用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是試驗品嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想啊 反正你死活也要硬闖尾張
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他是試用品還是什麼品的 能先為你派上用場也是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真一心求死的話也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若你已決心為了軍神無論如何也要活下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得似乎不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村啊 前去應戰便可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈發呈現萬馬奔騰之勢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便現在身死於此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也斷不會有一絲一毫悔意與悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這天下還不能交給這群毛頭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需忌憚 放手一搏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天佑吾身！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見啊 真田幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下已對此刻期待甚久 獨眼龍伊達政宗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速速與在下堂堂正正決一死戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你全部的氣勢讓我好好地享受一番吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 吾之魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party 還沒有結束！
