Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:42.23,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}沸き上がる情熱と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:47.43,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燻る魂が胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.89,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.41,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.80,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:04.26,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鋼の牙を起て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:12.83,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと聲を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:20.04,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:06.46,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下擊斷煩惱的扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.86,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫無用處的自尊在垃圾回收日捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:15.86,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}獵取一切的武士瘋狂起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:19.59,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃機頻頻轟鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.95,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍將延續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.11,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜爛的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:30.81,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在歎息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.69,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟隨神風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.23,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向著未知之處前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:42.23,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的熱情與
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:47.43,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}薰染的靈魂勒緊胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:51.89,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃燒的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.41,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.80,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷達之下尋找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:04.26,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}舉起鋼刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:12.83,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}縱情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:20.04,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}繼續這不羈的生命
